:1928983,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a6e14671b962f026e1ebd223695ca07ff95850c","tid":1928983,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"立場又癲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101d9476b5f71ee3a0def7e2390d422d680fc7dd","tid":1928983,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:34:19.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在全球肆虐，全球多國擬進一步限制出入境。歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩（Ursula von der Leyen）提倡，歐盟在未來 30 日暫停所有非必要外國人入境，建議仍有待歐盟各國領袖商討。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟明天將召開會議討論有關禁令，建議需要獲成員國支持通過。馮德萊恩周一表示，已告知七大工業國組織（G7）領導人這建議。措施初步計劃為期 30 日，但若有需要可以進一步延長，「越少旅行，我們就越能控制病毒，因此我建議國家元首和政府，對前往歐盟的非必要旅行實行臨時限制」。<br />\n<br />\n馮德萊恩稱在建議計劃之下，英國與歐盟之間仍然容許往來，而回國的歐盟公民、醫護人員、從事病毒研究的科學家等，都可以豁免。"},{"pid":"1979e6b53059458e70944bfc30c9b0fea136a68f","tid":1928983,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"地圖炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe33daf3042f19cfee6949dcfc38aa7f1e5a684","tid":1928983,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1979e6b53059458e70944bfc30c9b0fea136a68f","tid":1928983,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"地圖炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ho